subject: Certain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Nova Scotia Floods) Remission Order
precis: Certain Fees in Respect of the Issuance of Identity and Travel Documents (2023 Nova Scotia Floods) Remission Order in order to remit fees that were waived for Canadians and permanent residents affected by the Nova Scotia floods from July 22 to November 30, 2023.
